OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fmainly dry but cloudy evening then
OL,7,Fturning increasingly clear during the
OL,8,Fnight. Quite a cold night with light
OL,9,Fto moderate northeasterly breezes.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,12,Fgood spells of sunshine. Perhaps the
OL,13,Fodd shower in the northwest at first,
OL,14,Fand then later towards County Down.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,17,Fmainly dry with some sunny spells,
OL,18,Fsome showers in the north later.
OL,19,FCloudier with a few showers on Monday.
OL,20,FBreezy on Tuesday with sunny intervals
OL,21,Fand showers.
